Digital                               IBM
South Queensferry                     Greenock
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
NEC                                   Mitsubishi
Livingston                            Haddington
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
National Semiconductors               Compaq
Greenock                              Erskine
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
